<ab facs="#facs_132_r1l13">des <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> Vnd lat vns </ab>
