<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Fuchsmag, als ir uns nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hausfrawn und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Karl Colers und
                            <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gesellsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für uns besant und so
                            v<expan><ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit im davon gerett
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz er ewch selb sein antwurt schriftlich
                        tun sol, wie er die sache gehandelt hat. <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan> aber,
                        daz ir oder ewr hausfraw daran niht ein <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu im iht <expan>zu
                                sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir ewch oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> und
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hausfrawn
                            <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>m</expan> gewalt von dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg,</ex></expan> wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Und getrawn ewch wol, ir lat ewch des
                                <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>; das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. Und lat uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        antwurt <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en.</ex></expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> letare. </ab>
</div>
